    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "just sink? what does that even mean. are you saying i should just give up? because i feel like if i stop fighting, i'm just gonna disappear or something. it feels like the only way to stop the hurting is to just... not be here. do you think that's a crazy thing to feel?",
